cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.SD, cs.CL

The paper proposes a deep learning model for multimodal learning from temporal data, which involves video, audio, and sensor signals. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers deep learning and representation learning. The paper also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and multimodal learning (cs.MM) since it deals with video and audio data. Additionally, the paper involves signal processing (cs.SD) since it deals with sensor signals. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) since it deals with speech recognition.
